Description: Python modules to extend logging mechanism
 .
 This package includes the following executable binaries:
 - dch2speclog - converting a Debian changelog into log entries
   of a RPM spec file.
 - check-changelog - checking a CHANGELOG.md for syntax errors
   and prints some information about.

Package: python3-fb-logging
Architecture: all
Depends: python3-click,
         python3-semver,
         python3-six,
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${python3:Depends}
Description: Python modules to extend logging mechanism
  The following objects are supported by this package:
  - ColoredFormatter - for colored output on the system console
  - FbSysLogHandler - to avoid BOM errors in syslog messages
  - UnixSyslogHandler - to support logging via syslog on systems without
    /dev/log
  The following functions are supported by this package:
  - colorstr() - for colorizing messages
 .
 This package includes the Python3 modules for this package.

